pacemaker: pacemaker (High-Availability cluster resource manager)
pacemaker: 
pacemaker: Pacemaker is an advanced, scalable High-Availability cluster
pacemaker: resource manager.
pacemaker: 
pacemaker: You might also want to install corosync, pacemaker, resource-agents,
pacemaker: crmsh, fence-agents and eventually cluster-glue.
pacemaker: 
pacemaker: You must have a haclient group and hacluster user to run this script.
pacemaker:   groupadd -g 226 haclient
pacemaker:   useradd -u 226 -g 226 -c "Pacemaker" -d / -s /bin/false hacluster
